                <mxCell id="49" value="&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 102, 204));&quot;&gt;Error Handling &lt;/span&gt;in server component: - the clild page error just bubble up to the parent so the error page in the parent folder will handle all its nested pages errors or we can create different error page for every nested page&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;The same error can/will also handle the error in the &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 102, 204));&quot;&gt;client component&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" parent="50" vertex="1">
