                <mxCell id="43" value="Server component iwth page.tsx in nextjs, receives param and searchParams by defualt in their prop, but the &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 102, 204));&quot;&gt;param&lt;/span&gt; value will only come if components are under the dynamic route segment and the &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(0, 102, 204));&quot;&gt;serachParam&lt;/span&gt; is can alway be present because a url can alway have a query string" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" parent="38" vertex="1">
